nodes.text: This town was located on the planet Bogden's moon Bogg 4. Among the bustling streets of the town that were filled with various species from all over the galaxy was a tavern called The Bonny Bounty. The young bounty hunter Boba Fett traveled to this town in 22 BBY in search of Tyranus, the man who hired his father Jango Fett to be the prime clone for the Grand Army of the Republic.
